    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>No ads. Just pure arcade action.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Solo Defender</i> is a vertically scrolling space shooter where you take on waves of enemies and mini-bosses to liberate the Janera star system from the ruthless Kalae occupiers.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With a single-life challenge and escalating difficulty, each run delivers fast-paced, high-stakes gameplay. Battle across multiple planets, crush enemy fleets, and face off against powerful level bosses. The final showdown? A drone-spawning Mothership packed with the system’s deadliest foes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Uncover secrets by solving the Covert Ops puzzle and unlock a hidden level for an extra challenge.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect Gems by defeating enemies and completing stages. Spend them in the in-game garage to upgrade your ship with powerful enhancements. Gems persist across playthroughs—but are tied to your chosen difficulty.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Features:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fully customizable key bindings</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Four difficulty modes: Easy, Normal, Hard, Extreme</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Multiple mini-boss encounters</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Epic final boss battle</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Bonus abilities: Multi shot, Invincibility, Repair, and More...</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Steam Achievements</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Persistent Gem system for ship upgrades</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
